，导致农业生产收益难以有效保障。农业生产收入远低于二三产业，「种粮一年不如外出打工一月」。 二是农业基础设施薄弱，抵御自然灾害能力不足。三是经营主体实力不强，社会化服务相对滞后。四是年轻劳动力流失严重，农技人才较为紧缺。第五则是农业信贷融资困难，金融服务供给不足。第六个因素是补贴水平相对较低，农业发展激励有限。 为什么年轻人不愿种地？陕西省农业农村厅发调研报告剖析"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/640194768"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip86pkProj75KEAMaCTEwNDU0MzUxMyCV0aetBjAAOC5AB3IJNjQwMTk0NzY4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1705666497.629803", "card_id": "Q_479342111", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 574}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有哪些你过了很久之后才真正明白的道理？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-722aa0db02e4a2402a11c68b1c020436_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "70 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/479342111"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ip86pkProj75KEAMaCDY4ODAxODMwINvv1IgGMAA4kBBACHIJNDc5MzQyMTExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1705666497.630255", "card_id": "Q_639334248", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 41}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "过年不在家一个多月如何安置小猫咪呢？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ab28a5190de4435fdd3c72c56963756c_1440w.webp?sour